Configuring Route 53

Domain Registration:
    
    1- Search for and select a domain name that is available
    2- Fill out the Contact Details page
        :make note of the "Privacy Protection" option
    3- Review Details & Purchase:
    4- Complete Purchase amd wait for "domain registration process" to complete

Hosted Zones & Record Sets:

    1- Hosted Zones and selected the domain name just registered
    2- Create two type A record sets for you domain that route to ELB
    3- Create record set!

Registering Domain: https://docs.aws.amazon.com/Route53/latest/DeveloperGuide/registrar.html
Routing Traffic: https://docs.aws.amazon.com/Route53/latest/DeveloperGuide/routing-to-elb-load-balancer.html